WEBVTT

00:00:06.093 --> 00:00:11.651
I bow to all the seekers of absolute truth.

00:00:17.478 --> 00:00:26.609
At the very outset, I have to say that truth is truth.

00:00:28.464 --> 00:00:33.368
This absolute truth cannot be changed
because it is absolute.

00:00:33.958 --> 00:00:37.035
It cannot be transformed.

00:00:39.014 --> 00:00:42.578
It cannot be explained,

00:00:43.016 --> 00:00:46.551
because it cannot be described.

00:00:47.425 --> 00:00:50.935
Truth has to be experienced.

00:00:52.118 --> 00:00:54.779
It’s an experience.

00:00:55.268 --> 00:01:00.513
In Sanskrit language, we have a
word called 'Veda',

00:01:01.002 --> 00:01:03.002
comes from the word ‘Vida’.

00:01:03.678 --> 00:01:07.939
‘Vida’ means to know on your central nervous
system.

00:01:08.938 --> 00:01:12.076
Like, I can feel this.

00:01:12.413 --> 00:01:17.740
In the same way, you must know the truth on your
fingertips.

00:01:18.257 --> 00:01:23.179
‘Bodha' also, from where the word Buddha has come,

00:01:23.863 --> 00:01:28.288
is that enlightenment you have to feel it

00:01:28.288 --> 00:01:32.233
on your central nervous system.

00:01:37.396 --> 00:01:45.256
So this absolute truth is what it was

00:01:45.256 --> 00:01:47.412
and is and will be.

00:01:47.917 --> 00:01:51.760
But I would request you not to believe me,

00:01:51.895 --> 00:01:56.687
because this blind faith has
caused so much trouble to us.

00:01:57.176 --> 00:02:00.695
All the people are fighting
all over the world with this blind faith.

00:02:00.830 --> 00:02:05.879
They believe in this and
they believe in that, believe in that.

00:02:07.851 --> 00:02:11.557
This kind of faith is not going to help us.

00:02:12.012 --> 00:02:16.913
We have to feel it ourselves and experience it.

00:02:17.570 --> 00:02:20.665
Unless and until you experience,

00:02:20.834 --> 00:02:26.566
please don’t have faith in me or in Sahaja Yoga.

00:02:27.139 --> 00:02:30.787
Very important it is to understand

00:02:31.074 --> 00:02:36.154
that this absolute truth is beyond your mind.

00:02:39.947 --> 00:02:43.018
We think no end of our mind.

00:02:43.220 --> 00:02:48.579
And all those who came from my country,
as well as from your own country,

00:02:49.063 --> 00:02:52.524
to deceive you and make money out of you,

00:02:52.718 --> 00:02:57.920
have used their mind very well.

00:02:59.690 --> 00:03:02.499
And your mind could not detect it.

00:03:03.398 --> 00:03:06.038
Even today they are there.

00:03:08.274 --> 00:03:11.134
So for you to see what is the truth,

00:03:11.220 --> 00:03:16.032
you must know that you cannot purchase it with money.

00:03:19.466 --> 00:03:21.827
This is very difficult to digest.

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:24.352
Many people told me in America,

00:03:24.352 --> 00:03:29.757
“Mother you can never be successful,
you cannot get people

00:03:30.128 --> 00:03:36.982
because they just believe that the person who
doesn’t take money has no validity”.

00:03:37.718 --> 00:03:40.519
My experience was so horrible.

00:03:40.759 --> 00:03:43.999
In Boston they asked me in the television,

00:03:44.151 --> 00:03:46.413
“How many Rolls-Royces you have?”

00:03:46.784 --> 00:03:48.868
“I have none”.

00:03:50.242 --> 00:03:53.180
I said, “My husband has only one car”.

00:03:53.298 --> 00:03:55.298
“So, you are not in the business?”

00:03:55.379 --> 00:03:56.538
“No”.

00:03:56.836 --> 00:04:02.718
Then they said, “We cannot, we are sorry.
You have to be in the business”.

00:04:06.838 --> 00:04:12.246
So all these mental acrobats that
have been going on in this country.

00:04:13.217 --> 00:04:15.910
I’ve been hoping to come to Berkeley.

00:04:16.062 --> 00:04:21.034
That everybody told me that Berkeley
is a place where there are people

00:04:21.270 --> 00:04:25.472
who are truly seeking the truth,

00:04:25.725 --> 00:04:28.498
and they are revolutionary.

00:04:29.904 --> 00:04:35.673
They do not accept anything that is just established.

00:04:36.182 --> 00:04:39.671
Imagine after so many years, 27 years,

00:04:39.751 --> 00:04:44.286
I am coming to Berkeley where I was really very anxious to come.

00:04:48.605 --> 00:04:51.998
So now, the time has come

00:04:52.436 --> 00:04:57.585
that we have to know the truth.

00:04:58.108 --> 00:05:00.599
We have to know the absolute truth.

00:05:00.886 --> 00:05:03.899
I call it as a blossom time,

00:05:04.101 --> 00:05:10.246
because I find there are so many
seekers of truth all over the world.

00:05:12.169 --> 00:05:19.131
And this time has come for these flowers
to become the fruit.

00:05:21.302 --> 00:05:24.328
Very simple thing to understand,

00:05:24.648 --> 00:05:29.453
that this is done by a power within you,

00:05:29.453 --> 00:05:30.706
as explained to you.

00:05:31.566 --> 00:05:34.697
Whether you believe it or not, it is there.

00:05:35.460 --> 00:05:41.343
This power has to be awakened, that’s all.

00:05:41.781 --> 00:05:46.919
A very simple thing, journey of 3 to 4 feet, that's all.

00:05:47.493 --> 00:05:51.087
But such a simple thing people don’t want to accept.

00:05:51.441 --> 00:05:55.953
If you say, “Eat this way”,  they’ll say,
“No, why not this and this way?”

00:05:56.290 --> 00:05:58.581
Because of this mind.

00:05:59.542 --> 00:06:04.007
This mind is the one which has created real problems for us.

00:06:05.996 --> 00:06:09.371
I am told some gentleman is making big money by telling

00:06:09.371 --> 00:06:14.142
that how to project this mind here, and project mind there.

00:06:15.086 --> 00:06:17.706
It’s like a cocoon.

00:06:18.482 --> 00:06:22.450
In a cocoon, you dash here and dash there.

00:06:22.551 --> 00:06:24.544
You have to get out of it.

00:06:25.585 --> 00:06:29.448
When they said you are to be born again, clearly,

00:06:29.751 --> 00:06:33.188
that doesn’t mean that you put a

00:06:35.964 --> 00:06:39.453
sign board here: ‘born again’. No.

00:06:40.194 --> 00:06:45.218
Born again means something
has to happen to your consciousness,

00:06:45.404 --> 00:06:47.162
to your awareness.

00:06:47.246 --> 00:06:49.165
You have to be truthful about it.

00:06:49.452 --> 00:06:53.931
How can you be satisfied with something
which is not the truth?

00:06:56.312 --> 00:06:59.001
So, what is the truth?

00:07:00.147 --> 00:07:02.400
Truth, if you understand,

00:07:02.718 --> 00:07:05.799
is not this body, this mind,

00:07:05.883 --> 00:07:09.499
these emotions, these thoughts, and this ego.

00:07:09.887 --> 00:07:16.328
But it is that you are the pure Spirit.